  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Ermitage Du Lac offers excellent home comfort in a boutique hotel. It is the perfect accommodation for families and couples alike who are looking for that little something extra.</p>
<h2>Location</h2>
<p>The hotel has excellent views overlooking the frozen Lac Miroir. You are just a short walk to the restaurants and shops, and a two minute walk to the nearest lifts.</p>
<p>After a day on the slopes you can make the most of the hotel's ski valet service by dropping your skis and boots right by the slopes and changing into comfy shoes to explore the <a data-udi="umb://document/cc094a7f49b04e9a845adc78e3c77f10" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc094a7f49b04e9a845adc78e3c77f10}" title="Mont Tremblant">Mont Tremblant's</a> popular bars and restaurants.</p>
<p>If you haven't had enough of the snow, you can enjoy ice skating on the rink right next to the hotel.</p>
<h2>Home Comforts</h2>
<p>The hotel has a variety of rooms to fit all needs, from standard rooms to condos with fully equipped kitchens. Some rooms even have a fireplace to curl up in front of after a busy day on the slopes.</p>]]></description>
