  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard rooms </strong>sleep one to four guests with one queen bed plus double sofa bed</p>
<p><strong>Deluxe rooms </strong>are larger and well decorated, they have one double plus double sofa bed. They can sleep one to four guests.</p>
<p><strong>One-Bedroom Condo </strong>can sleep two to four and have one double or two queen beds, with double sofa bed in lounge area. They feature a balcony, microwave, fridge and most have a full kitchen and fireplace.</p>
